  scope:
    actor:
    - org
    data_domain: []
    context: []
  hazard: uncured material breach or violation by a business associate
  conditions:
  - organization knows of a pattern of activity or practice of the business associate
    that constituted a material breach or violation of the business associate's obligation
    under the contract or other arrangement
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - When the organization knows of such a pattern of activity or practice, the organization
    must take reasonable steps to cure the breach or end the violation, as applicable.
